   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="edition">
            <ab>
               <lb n="1"/>Μητρι ευχην.
               <lb n="2"/>
                  <persName>
                     <name key="Menios">Μηνιοσ</name>
                  </persName> 
                  <persName>
                     <name key="Menios">Μηνι<supplied reason="lost">ου</supplied></name>
                  </persName>
            </ab>
         </div>
         <div type="translation">
            <p>To the mother, a prayer. Menios, son of Menios.</p>
         </div>
         <div type="commentary">
            <p>The stele was originally much taller and was apparently cut down to its present size for reuse as a building block. Letters at the beginning of the second line are larger. Basis of verification: photo.</p>
         </div>
